  "title": "Event & Sales 🚀",
  "description": "<p><strong>Looking for a fun, social job with real growth?</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>Not into boring desk jobs? Prefer meeting new people, working in energetic environments, and learning useful skills while you go? This Events & Sales role is a great place to start.</p><p><br /></p><p>No experience needed — we’ll train you from day one 👍</p><p><br /></p><p><br /><u>What You’ll Be Doing</u></p><p>• Represent brands at events, roadshows, and pop-ups</p><p>• Chat with customers and share product info</p><p>• Help out with simple sales & marketing activities</p><p>• Work with a fun, supportive team on the ground</p><p>• Build confidence, communication, and people skills</p><p>• Earn through a performance-based / commission structure</p><p><br /></p><p></p><p><u>Who This Is For</u></p><p>• Fresh grads, students, or career switchers</p><p>• Friendly, positive, and open to learning</p><p>• Enjoys working with people (or wants to get better at it)</p><p>• Team players who like energetic environments</p><p><br /><br /></p><p><u>Why You’ll Enjoy It</u></p><p>• No desk, no routine — every day is different</p><p>• Training and guidance provided step by step</p><p>• Fun team culture with bonding and activities</p><p>• Opportunities to grow into leadership roles</p><p>• Travel opportunities for top performers ✈️</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>If you’re looking for a starter role that’s social, hands-on, and helps you grow, this could be a great fit.</p><p><br /></p><p>👉 Apply now / DM us to find out more</p>",
